ter Gastdirigent war er in ganz Europa unterwegs.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aConductors (Music)zHungaryvBiography. 7aMUSIC / General.2bisacsh  aSzenkar, Eugen, Oper, Operngeschichte.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2016z9783110485264oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783412502669423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783412502669.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DKUb2016